"<1.so>Oh! <2.pa>It's the Champion, Master Link!<3.pa>\n"
"How are things?\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>As for me, I'm here to protect <5.se_co>Sir Muzu<6.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
