msgctxt "Npc_Zora003_SD_010"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Yes, of course you wish to hear about\n"
"our dear <2.se_co>Mipha<3.re_co>.<4.pa> I am sure it would bring\n"
"her peace to know she is on your mind.\n"
"<5.se_co>Mipha<6.re_co> was always kind, from the day she\n"
"was born.<7.pa> She was equally as kind to her\n"
"own as she was to complete strangers.\n"
"<8.so>When you first took to visiting us,\n"
"back when you were but a child,\n"
"she adored you like a brother.\n"
"<9.so>However, as you know, Hylians age much\n"
"faster than us. Eventually you grew so\n"
"much, she began to look up to you...<10.pa>\n"
"<11.se_co><12.so><13.re_co>As <14.se_co>Mipha's Diary <15.re_co>plainly "
"states...<16.pa>it was\n"
"not long before she developed strong\n"
"feelings for you.\n"
"<17.so>A Zora princess falling in love with a\n"
"Hylian swordsman...\n"
"\n"
"<18.so>It reminds me of a Zora legend of old.\n"
"That is why I welcomed the idea of you\n"
"and <19.se_co>Mipha<20.re_co> becoming husband and wife.<21.pa>\n"
"<22.so>It is a shame you two never had the\n"
"chance to see what might have been...<23.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

