msgctxt "Npc_ZoraB001_SD_000"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Link! I must thank you for journeying all\n"
"this way! And, of course, for taming that\n"
"feisty Divine Beast Vah Ruta!\n"
"<2.so>You somehow overcame the objections\n"
"of the old geezers on our council,\n"
"all to help save our home!\n"
"<3.so>Yes, you are a treasure of a Hylian!\n"
"Taking time out of your journey to come\n"
"to our rain- and monster-ridden home!\n"
"<4.so>And here you activated those orbs with\n"
"<5.se_co>shock arrows<6.re_co>, freed <7.se_co>Ruta<8.re_co>, and "
"released\n"
"my sister from her lingering regret.\n"
"<9.so>Link...<10.pa> I simply can't thank you enough!\n"
"<11.so>Especially for following me to the end,\n"
"pushy and unreasonable as I am!\n"
"<12.so><13.se_co>Zora's Domain<14.re_co> would still be in peril if\n"
"not for you. <15.so>You are welcome anytime,\n"
"and we are ever at your service!\n"
"<16.so><17.te_si>Have I mentioned how incredible\n"
"you are? And how thankful I am?<18.ra><19.te_si><20.so>Because you are! "
"And I am! <21.pa>Yes, you are\n"
"the greatest of Hylians and my most\n"
"treasured friend for all time!\n"
"<22.so>Ah...<23.pa> You must forgive me.<24.pa> I am but a\n"
"rambling fool, wasting the time of my\n"
"cherished friend and hero of the Zora.\n"
"<25.so>I do hope you understand that I carry on\n"
"so only because I am ever so grateful\n"
"for all you have done and ever will do!\n"
"<26.so>But I digress. <27.pa>Link! <28.pa>Might I ask what\n"
"brings you to our beloved domain?<29.ch>"
msgstr ""

