msgctxt "Npc_ZoraB001_SD_010"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The sacred trial my sister challenged?\n"
"You are a keen one, Link!\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>I have recently noticed certain things\n"
"that last occurred when my dear sister,\n"
"<3.se_co>Mipha<4.re_co>, took the trial to master <5.se_co>Ruta<6.re_co>."
"\n"
"That is why I sent <7.se_co>Muzu<8.re_co> and <9.se_co>Tottika<10.re_co> "
"to\n"
"stand guard east of <11.se_co>Ulria Grotto<12.re_co>. It was\n"
"one of the areas associated with the trial.\n"
"<13.so>...Link! <14.pa>Yes, I have figured it out.<15.pa>\n"
"YOU are challenging the sacred trial!\n"
"I wish you luck, my friend."
msgstr ""

